#. lang="pi"><section class="sutta" id="dn7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p
#. class="division">
msgctxt "dn7:1.1"
msgid "Dīgha Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Long Discourses 7"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "dn7:2.1"
msgid "Jāliyasutta"
msgstr "With Jāliya"

#. </h1></div><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="wp" id="wp1"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts1.159"></a>
msgctxt "dn7:3.1"
msgid "<span class=\"evam\">Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​</span>"
msgstr "<span class=”evam”>So I have heard.</span>"

msgctxt "dn7:3.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery. "

msgctxt "dn7:3.3"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena dve pabbajitā—"
msgstr "Now at that time two renunciates—"

msgctxt "dn7:3.4"
msgid ""
"muṇḍiyo ca paribbājako jāliyo ca dārupattikantevāsī yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkamiṃsu;"
msgstr ""
"the wanderer Muṇḍiya and Jāliya the pupil of Dārupattika—came to the Buddha"

msgctxt "dn7:3.5"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu."
msgstr "and exchanged greetings with him."

msgctxt "dn7:3.6"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, they stood to one side"

msgctxt "dn7:3.7"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho te dve pabbajitā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr "and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "dn7:3.8"
msgid ""
"“kiṃ nu kho, āvuso gotama, taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīraṃ, udāhu aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ "
"sarīran”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Gotama, are the soul and the body the same thing, or they are "
"different things?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a>
msgctxt "dn7:4.1"
msgid "“Tena hāvuso, suṇātha sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "“Well then, reverends, listen and pay close attention, I will speak.” "

msgctxt "dn7:4.2"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti kho te dve pabbajitā bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Yes, reverend,” they replied."

msgctxt "dn7:4.3"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: <a class=\"wp\" id=\"wp2\"></a>“"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

msgctxt "dn7:4.4"
msgid "idhāvuso, tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ, sammāsambuddho …"
msgstr ""
"“Take the case when a Realized One arises in the world, perfected, a fully "
"awakened Buddha …"

msgctxt "dn7:4.5"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn7:4.6"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, āvuso, bhikkhu sīlasampanno hoti."
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is accomplished in ethics. …"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="pts" id="pts1.160"></a>
msgctxt "dn7:5.1"
msgid "…"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn7:5.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn7:5.3"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr "They enter and remain in the first absorption …"

msgctxt "dn7:5.4"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, āvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ jānāti evaṃ passati, kallaṃ nu kho tassetaṃ "
"vacanāya:"
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant knows and sees like this, would it be appropriate to say of "
"them:"

msgctxt "dn7:5.5"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vāti."
msgstr ""
"‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are are "
"different things’?”"

msgctxt "dn7:5.6"
msgid ""
"Yo so, āvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ jānāti evaṃ passati, kallaṃ tassetaṃ vacanāya:"
msgstr "“It would, reverend.”"

msgctxt "dn7:5.7"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn7:5.8"
msgid "Ahaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, evaṃ jānāmi evaṃ passāmi."
msgstr "“But reverends, I know and see like this."

msgctxt "dn7:5.9"
msgid "Atha ca panāhaṃ na vadāmi:"
msgstr "Nevertheless, I do not say:"

msgctxt "dn7:5.10"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vā …"
msgstr ""
"‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are are "
"different things’. …"

msgctxt "dn7:5.11"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

#. <a class="wp" id="wp4"></a><a class="wp" id="wp3"></a>
msgctxt "dn7:5.12"
msgid "dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ …"
msgstr "They enter and remain in the second absorption …"

msgctxt "dn7:5.13"
msgid "tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ …"
msgstr "third absorption …"

msgctxt "dn7:5.14"
msgid "catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr "fourth absorption."

msgctxt "dn7:5.15"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, āvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ jānāti evaṃ passati, kallaṃ nu kho tassetaṃ "
"vacanāya:"
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant knows and sees like this, would it be appropriate to say of "
"them:"

msgctxt "dn7:5.16"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vāti?"
msgstr ""
"‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are are "
"different things’?”"

msgctxt "dn7:5.17"
msgid ""
"Yo so, āvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ jānāti evaṃ passati kallaṃ, tassetaṃ vacanāya:"
msgstr "“It would, reverend.”"

msgctxt "dn7:5.18"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn7:5.19"
msgid "Ahaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, evaṃ jānāmi evaṃ passāmi."
msgstr "“But reverends, I know and see like this."

msgctxt "dn7:5.20"
msgid "Atha ca panāhaṃ na vadāmi:"
msgstr "Nevertheless, I do not say:"

msgctxt "dn7:5.21"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vā …"
msgstr ""
"‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are are "
"different things’. …"

msgctxt "dn7:5.22"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn7:5.23"
msgid "ñāṇadassanāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti …"
msgstr "They extend and project the mind toward knowledge and vision …"

msgctxt "dn7:5.24"
msgid ""
"yo kho, āvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ jānāti evaṃ passati, kallaṃ nu kho tassetaṃ "
"vacanāya:"
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant knows and sees like this, would it be appropriate to say of "
"them:"

msgctxt "dn7:5.25"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vāti."
msgstr ""
"‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are are "
"different things’?”"

msgctxt "dn7:5.26"
msgid ""
"Yo so, āvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ jānāti evaṃ passati kallaṃ tassetaṃ vacanāya:"
msgstr "“It would, reverend.”"

msgctxt "dn7:5.27"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn7:5.28"
msgid "Ahaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, evaṃ jānāmi evaṃ passāmi."
msgstr "“But reverends, I know and see like this."

msgctxt "dn7:5.29"
msgid "Atha ca panāhaṃ na vadāmi:"
msgstr "Nevertheless, I do not say:"

msgctxt "dn7:5.30"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vā …"
msgstr ""
"‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are are "
"different things’. …"

msgctxt "dn7:5.31"
msgid "pe …."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="wp" id="wp5"></a>
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn7:6.1"
msgid "…"
msgstr "…"

msgctxt "dn7:6.2"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn7:6.3"
msgid "Nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānāti."
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’ "

msgctxt "dn7:6.4"
msgid ""
"Yo kho, āvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ jānāti evaṃ passati, kallaṃ nu kho tassetaṃ "
"vacanāya:"
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant knows and sees like this, would it be appropriate to say of "
"them:"

msgctxt "dn7:6.5"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vāti?"
msgstr ""
"‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are are "
"different things’?”"

msgctxt "dn7:6.6"
msgid ""
"Yo so, āvuso, bhikkhu evaṃ jānāti evaṃ passati, na kallaṃ tassetaṃ vacanāya:"
msgstr "“It would not, reverend.”"

msgctxt "dn7:6.7"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn7:6.8"
msgid "Ahaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, evaṃ jānāmi evaṃ passāmi."
msgstr "“But reverends, I know and see like this."

msgctxt "dn7:6.9"
msgid "Atha ca panāhaṃ na vadāmi:"
msgstr "Nevertheless, I do not say:"

msgctxt "dn7:6.10"
msgid "‘taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīran’ti vā ‘aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīran’ti vā”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The soul and the body are the same thing’ or ‘The soul and the body are are "
"different things’.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a>
msgctxt "dn7:7.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "This is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "dn7:7.2"
msgid "Attamanā te dve pabbajitā bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr "Uplifted, the two renunciates approved of what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn7:8.1"
msgid "Jāliyasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
